[{"id":"e642c9a2598507ed","type":"tab","label":"[Mindmap] Wires, Pipes and Nodes","disabled":false,"info":"::: aim\n\nCreate a mindmap for an article concerning the difference between [Noisecraft](https://noisecraft.app/) flows and Node-RED flows.\n\n:::\n\n::: background\n\nBased on this [discussion](https://discourse.nodered.org/t/noisecraft-anyone-heard-of-it/79813/9?u=gregorius).\n\nTL;DR:\n\nNoisecraft uses a state machine, the flow is actually a description of the changes in the state of the machine. At each point in time the flow has a state.\n\nNode-RED is event driven and describes the changes to the data that flows through the flows. If there is no event, then there is no data and no flow.\n\n:::\n\n","env":[]},{"id":"2804d83f00f12df8","type":"Idea","z":"e642c9a2598507ed","name":"Wire, Pipes and Flows","info":"","sumPass":false,"sumPassPrio":0,"sumPassNodeId":"","createdAt":"2023-08-28T16:35:16.412Z","updatedAt":"2023-08-28T16:35:28.702Z","x":693,"y":1194,"wires":[["6e338f3c507acbce","36fafbdc7866bcf0"]]},{"id":"6e338f3c507acbce","type":"Thought","z":"e642c9a2598507ed","name":"State machine v. Event driven","info":"","sumPass":false,"sumPassPrio":0,"sumPassNodeId":"","createdAt":"2023-08-28T16:35:35.546Z","updatedAt":"2023-08-28T16:35:51.710Z","x":966,"y":1119,"wires":[["937e849a968b357d"]]},{"id":"937e849a968b357d","type":"Thought","z":"e642c9a2598507ed","name":"Stateless v. Stateful","info":"","sumPass":false,"sumPassPrio":0,"sumPassNodeId":"","createdAt":"2023-08-28T16:35:58.731Z","updatedAt":"2023-08-28T16:36:12.796Z","x":1224,"y":1164,"wires":[["0be96924c19659c4","ca989d906d25a998"]]},{"id":"36fafbdc7866bcf0","type":"Thought","z":"e642c9a2598507ed","name":"Shapes are the same, meaning is different","info":"","sumPass":false,"sumPassPrio":0,"sumPassNodeId":"","createdAt":"2023-08-28T16:36:27.767Z","updatedAt":"2023-08-28T16:43:10.987Z","x":987,"y":1304,"wires":[["a6634eb8981ab217"]]},{"id":"4747eb31010d8d00","type":"Thought","z":"e642c9a2598507ed","nam